scheme (`fastapi.security`) in `auth/services.py` |\n\nThe JWT algorithm used is `HS256` (HMAC-SHA256), configured in `app/settings.py`:\n```python\nJWT_ALGORITHM = \"HS256\"\n```\n\n---\n\n### 4. **Redis Support**\n\n| Library | Purpose |\n|---------|---------|\n| **`aioredis`** | Async Redis client (declared in `Pipfile`) |\n\nRedis is configured as a service in `docker-compose.yml` (`redis:alpine` image) and its connection parameters are set in `app/settings.py`:\n```python\nREDIS_HOST = environ.get(\"REDIS_HOST\", \"localhost\")\nREDIS_PORT = environ.get(\"REDIS_PORT\", \"6379\")\n```\n\n---\n\n### 5. **Other Notable Libraries & Tools**\n\n- **`pytest`** – Testing framework\n- **Pipenv** – Dependency management (`Pipfile` / `Pipfile.lock`)\n- **Docker / Docker Compose** – Containerization (3 services: `web`, `postgres`, `redis`)\n- **Python 3.9** – Target runtime (`python:3.9-slim-bullseye` base image)\n\n---\n\n### Summary Architecture\n\n```\nFastAPI (uvicorn)\n├── PostgreSQL (via SQLAlchemy + databases/asyncpg)\n│   └── Alembic (migrations)\n├── Redis (via aioredis)\n├── Auth: JWT (python-jose) + Password hashing (passlib/bcrypt)\n└── OAuth2PasswordBearer (FastAPI security)\n```", "additional_kwargs": {"refusal": null}, "response_metadata": {"token_usage": {"completion_tokens": 1023, "prompt_tokens": 9939, "total_tokens": 10962, "completion_tokens_details": {"accepted_prediction_tokens": null, "audio_tokens": null, "reasoning_tokens": 151, "rejected_prediction_tokens": null}, "prompt_tokens_details": {"audio_tokens": null, "cached_tokens": 9472}, "prompt_cache_hit_tokens": 9472, "prompt_cache_miss_tokens": 467}, "model_provider": "openai", "model_name": "deepseek-v4-pro", "system_fingerprint": "fp_9954b31ca7_prod0820_fp8_kvcache_20260402", "id": "46da981a-84ba-49cc-8d5f-975e215ceab3", "finish_reason": "stop", "logprobs": null}, "type": "ai", "name": null, "id": "lc_run--019ea3b2-6ab1-71f3-b432-f849facb2d77-0", "tool_calls": [], "invalid_tool_calls": [], "usag